{"tid":169964,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"［有圖］咁既情況係咪壞底板？","createTime":"2017-03-24T13:08:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T15:56:26.000Z","uid":8232,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3634169f41d555b041c69e148d584c696631256c","tid":169964,"uid":8232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T13:08:12.000Z","msg":"早幾日壞左張display <br />\n蚊左張卡用左兩日之後<br />\n我部機會係開唔到機 就算開到用左一陣佢會花畫面然後自動熄機 <br />\n有時boot緊都會花畫面熄機 通常畫面係隨機單色/全黑但左邊有一條野咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/55znh8f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F55znh8f.jpg&h=ed1f9be4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果要換既我換咩底板好？<br />\n用緊i5 3450加ddr3 ram<br />\n最好市面上仲有得買既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有如果自己砌唔到可唔可以拎返去中田俾錢幫手砌 已經過左保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔該晒巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"160153049180a70bb89bd7146e671a7fed9be146","tid":169964,"uid":8232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T13:29:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd8151a5b7397df066b9b07641b71786e276a3a5","tid":169964,"uid":8232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T13:58:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1514ad51d32bbb77bfe1690df7733e4b2d845f8f","tid":169964,"uid":76291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T14:02:53.000Z","msg":"巴打住邊，我平時整開電腦個間唔錯，介紹你去啦"},{"pid":"82af91e21516ab3b81bcaac7d1f28ceba17295d1","tid":169964,"uid":8232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T14:06:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打住邊，我平時整開電腦個